Package: MycoTools
Title: Tools for Mycoteam Sensor Data Processing
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Anders", "Nygaard", , "anders@anythings.no", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1922-0751")),
    person("ANYthings v/ Anders B. Nygaard", role = c("cph", "fnd")),
    person("Mycoteam AS", role = "cph")
  )
Description: Functions for importing, normalising, and analysing indoor
    climate and moisture sensor data from heterogeneous logger formats.
    Provides robust datetime parsing (unified or split date/time
    columns), sensor-ID normalisation, decimal-comma-aware numeric
    coercion, gap-filling on regular time intervals, season and
    ISO-week derivation, and the MYCOindex risk scoring system for
    mold, temperature, and wood moisture conditions. Developed by
    ANYthings (sole proprietorship of Anders B. Nygaard) for
    Mycoteam AS.
